Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想與希望成為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓動人們 轉動地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上太陽會升起並不代表會有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為人們抱有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的太陽才會升起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球 由我們來轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱鬥英雄 鋼巴戰隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:02:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽究竟是怎麼作曲的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 怎麼作曲...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是普通那樣來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那個 邊唱歌 還有唱歌什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本旋律就是從腦中產生的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邊考慮邊作曲麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將想像出來的旋律連接合起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是貓說不定也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣就可以了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢 我只是負責聽的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼著急忙慌的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢來不是蠻好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也許是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後也許問一下志保姐比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中的時候也在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 對啊 那樣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
