Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs74\c&H000000&\blur2\shad5\3c&HB8B8C4&\fad(640,0)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\b0\i1\4c&H606060&\pos(441,453)}變紅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然和馬有關的工作有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馴養師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做馴養師的話體重沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話不經大腦哦田中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊倒是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓別人騎上自己培養的馬奔跑什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然有些無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家久等了 有大事發表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將到來的白祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們合唱部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾是羽毛球部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想出演音樂劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音樂劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 不用說讓別人聽歌是主要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後有正經的故事劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有跳舞 還有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞臺也好好製作一下什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劇本我來寫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏現在在作曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個作為主題曲來唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏在作曲麼 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 還完全沒頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能做好都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽來編舞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,編舞？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你運動神經好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中和維也納去做大小道具的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服飾就由大家來想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是很認真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說認真過頭了呢還是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會花錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會要以萬為單位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白祭的援助費有那麼多嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道有什麼別的方法麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是現在大家要考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己想好了再說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌是好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛啊戀啊 尋死覓活的可不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可千萬別說要加吻戲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會說啊 維也納也說點啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個... 說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常一樣 好好的聽大家說 記好筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 筆記就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 紗羽 最近志保姐忙不忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽？ 我想跟平時一樣
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
