Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}『讓殘夏熱鬧起來』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請閱覽下手中的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於西端商店街全體的營業額
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和去年同期相比 今年情況略微有點嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也是 現如今的時代果然有點困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體也有點跟不上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂崎先生都住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入院檢查身體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 那個人特別貪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請注意保持安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了啦 說明看了就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不過總之還是先說明下然後再考慮對策
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後也只能踏踏實實一點點努力做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏實幹活就是最好的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榮光堂不是有個年輕的媳婦兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當地英雄秀如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當地英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道 就是吉祥物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉祥物只是個玩偶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要展出英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出紅 白 黃 綠等等的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展出英雄 比如說？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊做著什麼什麼英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼戰隊之類的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊派送商店的宣傳傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 東西屋
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an7}注：東西屋\N_____________\N是指藝人到主顧指定的地方或店鋪去表演，用以宣傳店鋪。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是挺好的嗎 志保小姐的想法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於服裝我心裡有數
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就是誰來演英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上的疲勞一直沒消啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少三人 可以的話五人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有哪位願意為了商店街獻身...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 媽媽 今天這之後有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏好像有事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 難道說你們是從社團回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們五個都在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家都過來吧 有很好吃的蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要來哦 我等著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊準備好吃的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 有好吃的蛋糕的話 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？啊 嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}那田中和我們一起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}維也納和來夏坐電車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問了志保阿姨就能寫歌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽到底是怎樣想 想著什麼事情創造出來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕？什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是能不能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到但是沒問題嗎之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不再多知道些媽媽的事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能一起寫歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好深奧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那笑容是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個 想要錢不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奶奶給我說過 不要坐過山車也不要相信太好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不想做回英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}制服&面具（活動用英雄服裝）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服和面具？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄制服
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}紅 粉 黃 白 綠 和鋼巴戰隊一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 看上去還能用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 這是怎麼回事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}這個會不會有點小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}料子很軟 彈性很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}啊 還有鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}雖然很舊 但是尺寸沒問題
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}這個彈性真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商店街辦過站臺便當大會 在那裡用過的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在站臺便當大會上？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 因為玩的太過 企劃失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是相撲大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an7}注:幕の內\N______________\N 有便當和相撲大賽的意思，這裡志保用相撲中的推倒和企劃的失敗一語雙關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷笑話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 想讓大家週末來幫忙 三萬如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五個人都要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上幾點開始 一天工作幾個小時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是湊夠五個人比較理想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出場是一次10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後一天出場五次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣週末三萬算是不錯的打工了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習也需要時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來決定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得來幫忙 是我女兒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏說想打聽她母親的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就以那個做交換條件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 英雄只能拜託你們幾個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是深具意義的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何具有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為會帶給人們希望和夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想和希望成為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推動人們轉動地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維也納？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是朝日升起所以明日才到來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們懷抱著希望生存著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以朝日才會升起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球由我們來轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了最重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己失去希望要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請再給我說一次成為英雄的條件
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}啊 那個 週末一場10分鐘 一天五場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他之前是這麼燃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鋼巴雷特的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱鬥英雄 鋼巴雷特戰隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的房間裡不就有麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是開關啟動了呀 英雄的開關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣決定了可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就決定早上在我家練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥的時間就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真昼前輩的作曲方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直只是唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以雖然是很好說話的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻是沒有談到過這個話題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過倒沒怎麼見她煩惱過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是靠突然的靈感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 要是以前多問問該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 要問作曲方法的話 去找教頭老師就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磁帶裡錄的歌就是和奏的媽媽和教頭老師一起寫的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真昼前輩說要寫屬於我們自己的歌的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都覺得是玩笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高倉前輩是很認真的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時也加入進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正完成的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們紛紛訝異道「還真的寫成了呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是首好歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高倉前輩雖然有些難捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我仍覺得她是很好的前輩 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫了我這麼多真是太感謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考慮了下英雄的設定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,設定？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西之端英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強手...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是商嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商店戰隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西之端商店街的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還直接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西之端英雄商店戰隊是維護銀河的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及保證顧客安全和幸福的正義使者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉類紅 水果粉 沙丁魚白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要穿這個嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}沒錯 其實西之端商店戰隊是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你選哪個顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡紅色吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽 紅色代表領導者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是喜歡哪個顏色就是哪個這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 紗羽要是有做紅色的覺悟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會乾脆地把紅色讓給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過在此之前我想確認你是否有做紅色的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的資格是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有非它不可 維也納穿紅色就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我選黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那宮本就是咖喱黃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商店街沒有咖喱店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是想讓和奏寫主題歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你還要做白祭的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想就用鋼巴戰隊的主題曲好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是出場的口號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量 接受 能量 充電 肉類紅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,產地直送 新鮮的美味 沙丁魚白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 再帥一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子小朋友們可不買帳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個 紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維他命 纖維 營養素 維持健康的蔬菜綠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再投入點感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會一個一個指導的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個 和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏你先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最愛咖喱 咖喱黃 砰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吥嚕—— 像這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託認真點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便只是鎮上的小型走秀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為孩子們的英雄可是超級重大的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是幫把手而已 這樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航空信？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是退回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄給在維也納的朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公寓的新主人說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個叫楊的人已經不在那裡了所以不要再寄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機裡有接到電話或者短信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楊只是個今年才要滿7歲的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們倆一起看過無數遍叔叔送來的鋼巴戰隊的錄像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼巴雷特是楊和我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我就準備回日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變得很寂寞呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼巴雷特會保護楊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了日本之後，會給我寫信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想知道日本的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 當然會了！·
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 維也納...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文武兩道之類的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奮起一發什麼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校的下面有白色的犀牛之類的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都寫進信裏了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然全部被退回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...維也納...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得會再見到楊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前相信楊在努力所以我也要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為西之端英雄 紅 努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我想到新的動作了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,產地直送 新鮮的美味 沙丁魚白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比剛才好很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 很有沙丁魚的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼...表現得更加新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這個不帶裙子誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看光光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計原本就是男性角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽身材很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內褲什麼的基本看不出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒裙子也不要緊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我們家大殿的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺院臭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快點喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快就換好了嗎？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開的話打飛你喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 破了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在幹嘛啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說是吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是前途多難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 我也是反對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說我是校長 但是我也是被雇傭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的指令...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太無法相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:20:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太突然了吧 這麼不負責任的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經妥協了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為合唱部的顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所經歷的那些回憶 已經忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浜坂高中校規第十八條
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生除了不得已的情況外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止打工
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有特殊情況就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 為了白祭而打工真是了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教頭會這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是想也沒用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教頭老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來申請打工的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合唱部為了白祭無論如何都需要更多的費用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有足夠的部費的話就沒必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們合唱部和聲樂不不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一丁點錢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有特殊情況的話 打工也可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就是那個特殊情況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要請您在打工申請書上蓋章...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好簡單呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}意外得爽快的蓋章了呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}遊刃有餘啦 這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不覺得奇怪嗎？ 教頭她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿著那衣服就來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,營養液 噴射
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}第十話 賣萌 燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱...拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芒果...射線！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,節奏和時間點都太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
